ut the required documents to be submitted to the Company.<br \\/>\\r\\n        c.\\tThe Member must declare that all of the information provided \\r\\nis complete and correct, including the information of sponsoring member \\r\\nof the Company.\\r\\n    <\\/p>\\r\\n    <p>\\r\\n        The Member agrees and acknowledges that the registration as \\r\\nmembership of the Company is subject to the approval by the Company. \\r\\nAfter the Company thoroughly reviews the information and documents \\r\\nprovided by the registrant, the process of the membership will be \\r\\ncompleted.\\r\\n    <\\/p>\\r\\n    <p>\\r\\n        The Company reserves the right to review information provided \\r\\nfor membership registration for any duration. Access to the website \\r\\nafter registration does not guarantee the acceptance of the membership \\r\\nby the Company.\\r\\n    <\\/p>\\r\\n    <p>\\r\\n        An initial duration of membership period begins from the date of\\r\\n the approval on registration and continues until the last day of twelve\\r\\n (12) month. If a Member has records of purchase of the Company\\u2019s \\r\\nproducts during this period, the duration of the membership will be \\r\\nextended by twelve (12) months, and thereafter.\\r\\n    <\\/p>\\r\\n    <p>\\r\\n        Moreover, in order to extend membership of the Company, a \\r\\nforeign applicant for membership must provide required information such \\r\\nas passport, staying visa in the Cambodia valid for at least one (1) \\r\\nyear in order to maintain its membership with the Company. Failure to \\r\\nprovide those required documents can constitute the membership \\r\\ncancellation.\\r\\n    <\\/p>\\r\\n    <p>\\r\\n        4. Passport and Visa Requirements:<br \\/>\\r\\n        a.\\tVisa information for foreigners residing in Cambodia must be \\r\\nprovided to and validated by the Company at least ten (10) days before \\r\\nthe visa expiration date.<br \\/>\\r\\n        b.\\tPassport information for foreigners residing in Cambodia must\\r\\n be provided to and validated by the Company at least ten (10) days \\r\\nbefore the passport expiration date.<br \\/>\\r\\n        c.\\tIf the Member whose visa or passport information has expired \\r\\ndoes not renew and hasn\\u2019t provided to company before ten (10) days, \\r\\nhis\\/her status changes to consumer member. He\\/she can only purchase \\r\\nAtomy products and cannot generate or earn commission fees from the \\r\\nCompany. To reestablish standing as business member, the Member must \\r\\ncontact and provide recertification documents to the Company branch \\r\\noffice.<br \\/>\\r\\n        If a member whose visa or passport has expired and does not \\r\\nrenew or provide to the Company ten (10) days before the expiration \\r\\ndate, his\\/her status will change to consumer membership.  Consumer \\r\\nmembers can purchase Atomy products but will not generate or earn \\r\\ncommission from the Company.  To reestablish business membership, the \\r\\nmember must contact and provide recertification documents to Atomy \\r\\nCambodia.\\r\\n    <\\/p>\\r\\n    <p>\\r\\n        5. Termination and Rejoining Membership:<br \\/>\\r\\n        The Member may withdraw his\\/her membership from the Company at \\r\\nany time and for any reason. The membership of the Company will be \\r\\nwithdrawn upon receipt and verification of completed termination form \\r\\nfrom the Member who wants to terminate his\\/her membership. Rejoining the\\r\\n membership of the Company can only be done one year after the \\r\\nwithdrawal from the membership of the Company.<br \\/>\\r\\n        The Company reserves the right to terminate or impose penalty on\\r\\n the Member who has infringed any one of the Company\\u2019s Rules stated \\r\\nbelow:\\r\\n    <\\/p>\\r\\n    <p>\\r\\n        6. Changes to Contact and Bank Account Details:<br \\/>\\r\\n        The Member must inform the Company of any change made to his\\/ \\r\\nher bank account and contact details which was provided to the Company. \\r\\nThe Company will bear no responsibility if the Member failed to receive \\r\\ncommission or any notices from the Company.\\r\\n    <\\/p>\\r\\n    <p>\\r\\n        7. Inheritance:<br \\/>\\r\\n        Upon the death of the Member, the Member\\u2019s interest may pass on \\r\\nto his\\/her relatives or designated person, subject to acceptance of the \\r\\nCompany in compliance with the Company\\u2019s Rules.\\r\\n    <\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/div>\"}', '2020-12-01 01:29:59', '2021-10-07 11:29:56'),
